{
  "texts": [
    "The lattice of the rectangle R z 1,...,z k i 0,i 1,...,i k-1 corresponds precisely to the lattice that appears in statement (ii) of the aforementioned lemma after the identification of R z 1,...,z k i 0,i 1,...,i k-1 with [0, c K] × [0, c] d-1 via a translation.",
    "Lemma 5.12.",
    "Let k ∈ N ∪ {0}.",
    "Then R k ⊃ R k+1.",
    "Suppose Q is an admissible cube of order k. Then L d (Q \\ R k+1) ≥ L d (Q)(1 - 1 K d-1).Proof."
  ]
}